<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Password Reset - Prof Bioresearch</title>
</head>

<body
    style="margin:0; padding:24px; background-color:#f4f6f9; color:#333; font-family:'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; -moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;">

    <div
        style="max-width:600px; margin:auto; background-color:#ffffff; padding:32px; border-radius:10px; box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">

        <!-- Header -->
        <h1 style="color:#0056b3; margin-top:0; text-align:center; font-size:26px; font-weight:700;">
            Password Reset Request
        </h1>

        <!-- Body -->
        <p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>We received a request to reset your password for your <strong>Prof Bioresearch</strong> employee account.</p>

        <p>Your one-time reset code is:</p>
        <div
            style="font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; text-align:center; color:#ffffff; background:#0056b3; padding:14px 20px; border-radius:6px; letter-spacing:2px; margin:20px 0;">
            {{code}}
        </div>

        <p>Please use this code to complete your password reset. For security reasons, it will expire after <strong>30
                minutes</strong>.</p>

        <p>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email — your account will remain secure.
        </p>

        <p>Best regards,<br /><strong>The Prof Bioresearch IT Team</strong></p>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div
            style="margin-top:40px; font-size:12px; color:#777; text-align:center; border-top:1px solid #e6e9ef; padding-top:20px;">
            &copy; {{year}} Prof Bioresearch · All rights reserved<br />
            <a href="https://www.profbioresearch.com"
                style="color:#0056b3; text-decoration:none;">www.profbioresearch.com</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>